description: Tyson TenZ Ngo (born May 5, 2001) is a Canadian player of Vietnamese descent who currently plays for Sentinels. He is a former Counter-Strike: Global Offensive player known for being on Cloud9.

Shahzeb ShahZaM Khan (born October 8, 1993) is an American player who currently plays for Sentinels. He is a former Counter-Strike: Global Offensive player who is mostly known for his time in Cloud9, OpTic and Complexity Gaming.
Michael dapr Gulino (born January 1, 1999) is an American player who currently plays for Sentinels. He is a former professional Counter-Strike: Global Offensive player.

Hunter SicK Mims (born September 2, 1998) is an American player who currently plays for Sentinels. He is a former professional Counter-Strike: Global Offensive player who was most known for his time in TSM and later on in Misfits.
